headline.main: Berlin's Long-Delayed Airport Gets New Boss
headline.print_headline: Berlin's Long-Delayed Airport Gets New Boss

lead_paragraph: The essays in David Shields’s “Other People” reveal him to be an elusive, humorous ironist particularly interested in sex, sports, selfhood, actors and fiction.
